photo.alt: A screenshot of a chaotic scene in the show Community, with different people labeled different things: Jeff (labeled as Twitter) holding an on-fire sleeve (labeled societal collapse) next to Troy (labeled as me) holding a pizza box (labeled The Queen's Corgi's) next to Britta (labeled Harry Styles spitting on Chris Pine), with a trio on the floor (labeled Lea Michele can't read/is somehow in Funny Girl, Sans. vs Reigen for Tumblr Sexyman, and Queen Elizabeth II) next to a fire labeled "the first week of September." There are also various objects labeled "Olivia Wilde trying to hide whatever the fuck happened on Don't Worry Darling," "it's literally 120 degrees in California," and "Paramore is back???"
